BLAPIECE DIGITAL ART AND 3D MODELING

BLAPIECE futuristic vision is to use art in all it's form.


Blapiece creates genuinely collectable ‘pieces’ to add to your ‘wardrobe’ and soon your home. Together, with you, we are creating your uniquely recognisable and distinctive style.
Those ‘in the know” will appreciate the colour, the texture, the silhouette and the quality down to the finest detail –- that it is an Individually numbered piece in a limited series.
collaborative art sessions where people are invited to paint into a painting game
finished painting made by 8 people, each person made a symbol and repeated 3 times for a pattern
after the pattern is made, the filling and painting begins. the painting game is a suggestion but not mandatory, artistic expression is always respected
the beginning of the painting process, each person took a turn to draw a symbol each turn for 3 rounds
